{"tid":1578641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"靜坐抗議係咪搞唔到","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T08:24:10.000Z","uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20ff041016a5614e97efd09f3fdabffab64c714f","tid":1578641,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:17:05.000Z","msg":"有一種抗爭方法，我聽過兩次<br />\n一次係啤梨晚報<br />\n一次係721之後去元朗警署市民分享<br />\n<br />\n就係原本由維園行去中環嘅遊行<br />\n同一條路 一二百萬人<br />\n由原本嘅行路<br />\n改為由維園開始坐喺度<br />\n一路沿住條路咁坐<br />\n塞到去中環<br />\n全部坐喺度<br />\n<br />\n咁樣又和平<br />\n威力亦好大<br />\n<br />\n咁耐以黎都無實現過<br />\n係咪有人諗到咁樣唔work?"},{"pid":"7ca710ccbfc054c48a0f87200ad67f826900f052","tid":1578641,"uid":55669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"想像左下, 係咪佔中咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a759d59e801768746f20cddad64ea81321f58b2","tid":1578641,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"坐到夜晚走淨幾千<br />\n水炮車一黎走淨幾百<br />\n速龍一衝拉幾十"},{"pid":"ad91c2aef38213a60a453abde48789119d255ed9","tid":1578641,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ca710ccbfc054c48a0f87200ad67f826900f052","tid":1578641,"uid":55669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"想像左下, 係咪佔中咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:24:10.000Z","msg":"都似，不過坐密啲<br />\n喺元朗講嘅果個哥哥仔<br />\n我記得佢建議咁樣全民坐到政府即時正面回應，否則變相佔住條路一直唔散"}]}